    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Octpress-画像保存先]]></title>
    <link href="http://blackhawk888.github.io/blog/2016/09/03/octpress-img/"/>
    <updated>2016-09-03T21:42:43+00:00</updated>
    <id>http://blackhawk888.github.io/blog/2016/09/03/octpress-img</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Octopressでこのブログを投稿するときに画像を挿入する場合はGyazoを使っていたが、
Octopressのディレクトリ指定の仕方は<a href="http://octopress.org/docs/plugins/image-tag/">公式ブログ</a>に書いてるとおり以下の設定をすればOK</p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Syntax </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;[class names]&quot;</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;/path/to/image&quot;</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;[width] [height] [title text [alt text]]&quot;</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<!--more-->


<h3>Examples</h3>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Syntax </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;&lt;a&quot;</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;href=&quot;</span><span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">placekitten</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">890</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">280</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;http://placekitten.com/890/280&lt;/a&gt;&quot;</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;left &lt;a&quot;</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;href=&quot;</span><span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">placekitten</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">320</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">250</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;http://placekitten.com/320/250&lt;/a&gt;&quot;</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;Place Kitten #2&quot;</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;right &lt;a&quot;</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;href=&quot;</span><span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">placekitten</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">300</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">500</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;http://placekitten.com/300/500&lt;/a&gt;&quot;</span> <span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;150&quot;</span> <span class="n">height</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;250&quot;</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;Place Kitten #3&quot;</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;right &lt;a&quot;</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;href=&quot;</span><span class="ss">http</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">placekitten</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">300</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">500</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;http://placekitten.com/300/500&lt;/a&gt;&quot;</span> <span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;150&quot;</span> <span class="n">height</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;250&quot;</span> <span class="n">title</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;&amp;lsquo;Place Kitten #4&amp;rsquo; &amp;lsquo;An image of a very cute kitten&amp;rsquo;&quot;</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>Octopressと同じサイト内で画像を挿入させるには、通常<code>source/images/</code>に画像を入れ、</p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Syntax </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;/images/exsample.png&quot;</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p><img src="/images/exsample.png" width="300" height="400">
<img class="right" src="/images/exsample02.png" width="300" height="400"></p>

<h3>Markdown形式の場合は</h3>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Markdown </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;image%20URL&quot;</span> <span class="n">alt</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;alt title&quot;</span> <span class="sr">/&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>絶対指定をすると</p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Markdown </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;https://blackhawk888.github.io/images/exsample.png&quot;</span> <span class="n">alt</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;exsample&quot;</span> <span class="sr">/&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p><img src="https://blackhawk888.github.io/images/exsample.png" alt="exsample" /></p>

<p>相対指定をすると</p>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>Markdown </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">img</span> <span class="n">src</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;/images/exsample02.png&quot;</span> <span class="n">alt</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;exsample&quot;</span> <span class="sr">/&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p><img src="/images/exsample02.png" alt="exsample" /></p>
]]></content>
